&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;As a Senior Manager of Business Development, you will hire, onboard, and mentor Business Development Representatives (BDRs) in your region, ensuring their success at GitLab. You&#39;ll partner closely with the sales team, and ultimately drive pipeline and results. In this role, you will report to the Director, Business Development (EMEA).&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
